<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 21:13:14 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>杜邦公司将分拆为三个独立公司</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/dupont-separate-into-three-independent-companies-2024-05-22/</link><description>杜邦公司周三表示，将分拆为三个上市公司，导致其股价在盘后交易中上涨 5%。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 21:10:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/dupont-separate-into-three-independent-companies-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，因国家监管机构审查而推迟波音向中国交付</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/boeing-deliveries-china-delayed-by-state-regulator-review-source-says-2024-05-22/</link><description>一位知情人士告诉路透社，由于中国监管机构对驾驶舱语音记录器相关电池进行审查，波音向中国的飞机交付最近几周被推迟。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 19:52:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/boeing-deliveries-china-delayed-by-state-regulator-review-source-says-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>美国立法者提出法案，以更容易遏制人工智能模型的出口</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-lawmakers-advance-bill-make-it-easier-curb-exports-ai-models-2024-05-22/</link><description>众议院外交事务委员会周三以压倒性多数票通过了一项法案，该法案将使拜登政府更容易限制人工智能系统的出口，理由是担心中国可能利用这些系统来增强其军事能力。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 17:01:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-lawmakers-advance-bill-make-it-easier-curb-exports-ai-models-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>中国地方政府机构要求恒大电动汽车公司返还2.624亿美元补贴</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-local-bodies-ask-evergrande-ev-unit-return-2624-mln-subsidy-2024-05-22/</link><description>中国恒大新能源汽车周三表示，其子公司已收到中国地方行政机构的一封信，要求偿还作为补贴和奖励提供的19亿元人民币（2.6242亿美元）。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 14:19:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-local-bodies-ask-evergrande-ev-unit-return-2624-mln-subsidy-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>法国七国集团需要在中国产能过剩问题上团结一致</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/g7-needs-stand-united-chinese-overcapacity-france-2024-05-22/</link><description>法国财政部长布鲁诺·勒梅尔周三在与七国集团同行举行会议之前表示，面对中国在电动汽车电池等关键行业的产能过剩，七国集团经济强国需要团结起来。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 13:04:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/g7-needs-stand-united-chinese-overcapacity-france-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>中国多个城市大幅降低还款额和抵押贷款利率以刺激房地产需求</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/several-chinese-cities-slash-down-payments-mortgage-rates-boost-property-demand-2024-05-22/</link><description>据官方媒体报道，中国多个城市降低了首付和抵押贷款利率，以应对最新一波刺激低迷房地产需求的刺激措施。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 11:20:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/several-chinese-cities-slash-down-payments-mortgage-rates-boost-property-demand-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>英国国防部长称中国正在努力向俄罗斯提供致命援助</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk-defence-minister-says-china-working-supply-lethal-aid-russia-2024-05-22/</link><description>英国国防部长格兰特·沙普斯周三指责中国向俄罗斯提供或准备向俄罗斯提供致命援助，用于其对乌克兰的战争。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 10:46:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk-defence-minister-says-china-working-supply-lethal-aid-russia-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>Temu母公司拼多多控股第一季度营收超出预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/temu-operator-pdd-holdings-beats-first-quarter-revenue-estimates-2024-05-22/</link><description>拼多多控股周三超出了第一季度收入预期，这得益于其国际购物网站 Temu 以及消费者对其中国折扣电子商务平台拼多多日益增长的兴趣。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 10:42:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/temu-operator-pdd-holdings-beats-first-quarter-revenue-estimates-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>格罗西表示，伊朗总统去世推迟了与国际原子能机构的谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/death-irans-president-has-delayed-talks-with-iaea-grossi-says-2024-05-22/</link><description>伊朗总统和外交部长在直升机失事中丧生，导致联合国核监督机构与德黑兰就改善与该机构合作的谈判暂停，该机构负责人拉斐尔·格罗西周三对路透社表示。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 10:39:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/death-irans-president-has-delayed-talks-with-iaea-grossi-says-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>新兴市场信用评级终于再次回升</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/emerging-market-credit-ratings-are-finally-looking-up-again-2024-05-22/</link><description>从巴西、尼日利亚和土耳其，甚至到埃及和赞比亚等一些风险最高的新兴市场，越来越多的证据表明，长达十年的主权信用评级恶化终于开始扭转。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 10:12:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/emerging-market-credit-ratings-are-finally-looking-up-again-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：英伟达临近，英国 CPI 大幅上涨未达到目标</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-05-22/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 10:04:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>流亡中国商人郭文贵因诈骗罪受审</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/exiled-chinese-businessman-guo-wengui-goes-trial-fraud-2024-05-22/</link><description>对流亡中国商人郭文贵的刑事审判将于周三开始陪审团遴选，美国检察官指控郭文贵诈骗数千名投资者和支持者超过 10 亿美元。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 10:04:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/exiled-chinese-businessman-guo-wengui-goes-trial-fraud-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>中国对12家与美国军方有联系的公司采取措施</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-takes-measures-against-12-us-military-linked-firms-2024-05-22/</link><description>中国周三表示，已对参与美国军工联合体的12家公司及其高管采取措施，以回应美国武装台湾和制裁中国企业。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 09:56:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-takes-measures-against-12-us-military-linked-firms-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>中国老板拖欠付款后橡树资本接手国际米兰</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/soccer-oaktree-says-it-has-taken-ownership-inter-milan-after-missed-payment-2024-05-22/</link><description>美国投资基金橡树资本管理公司 (Oaktree Capital Management) 表示，在意大利足球冠军国际米兰 (Inter Milan) 的中国大股东未能支付 3.95 亿欧元（合 4.28 亿美元）的款项后，该公司已收购了该俱乐部的所有权。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 09:36:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/soccer-oaktree-says-it-has-taken-ownership-inter-milan-after-missed-payment-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>英国国防部长称情报有证据表明中国向俄罗斯提供致命援助</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk-defence-minister-says-intelligence-has-evidence-chinese-lethal-aid-russia-2024-05-22/</link><description>英国国防部长格兰特·沙普斯周三指责中国向俄罗斯提供或准备向俄罗斯提供致命援助，供莫斯科在对乌克兰的战争中使用。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 09:28:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk-defence-minister-says-intelligence-has-evidence-chinese-lethal-aid-russia-2024-05-22/</guid></item></channel></rss>